parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corroded front brake lines can cause brake fluid leaks, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Brake fluid leaking onto the ground
failed inspection due to corroded front brake lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS failure can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of control.
symptoms: ABS activates during normal stops on dry pavement
anti-lock brakes engage at slow stops
causing longer stopping lengths
abnormal rear disc brake operation and wear factor on both rear wheels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the ABS electronic module can cause the ABS system to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, increased risk of accidents, and potential loss of control.
symptoms: Failure of the under-dash ABS electronic module
failure of the ABS system
which can result in accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A sticky accelerator pedal can cause unintended acceleration, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal feels sticky or hesitant
the vehicle accelerates unintentionally
the pedal is difficult to press or release
the pedal has a slow return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure to Disclose Technical Service Bulletin (TSB) Information
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to disclose TSB information can lead to delayed or avoided repairs, potentially causing harm to drivers and passengers due to unaddressed safety issues.
symptoms: Dealership or repair shop denies knowledge of TSB
refuses to perform repairs under TSB
or misleads customers about the existence of TSB.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The simultaneous failure of tailgate cables can cause severe pinching of the hand, leading to swelling and pain, which can result in injury and potentially long-term damage.
symptoms: The tailgate cables break simultaneously
causing the tailgate to shut abruptly
pinching the hand
resulting in swelling and pain.
